{{> layout/header}}

<style>
    .page-header { background: #fff; border-bottom: 1px solid #eaecf4; padding: 40px 28px 28px; }
    .page-header-inner { max-width: 1140px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .page-title { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 900; color: #1c1e26; letter-spacing: -0.5px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .page-desc { font-size: 14px; color: #9ca3af; }
    .list-section { padding: 36px 28px 80px; }
    .list-inner { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .expert-summary { background: #fff; border: 1.5px solid #eaecf4; border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; margin-bottom: 28px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 18px; }
    .expert-avatar { width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 50%; background: #eff6ff; border: 2px solid #bfdbfe; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 24px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .expert-info { flex: 1; }
    .expert-name { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 800; color: #1c1e26; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .cert-badge { font-size: 10px; background: #fffbeb; color: #b45309; border: 1px solid #fde68a; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: 700; }
    .expert-career { font-size: 13px; color: #9ca3af; }
    .expert-rating-box { text-align: center; }
    .rating-big { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 900; color: #1c1e26; letter-spacing: -1px; }
    .rating-stars { color: #f59e0b; font-size: 18px; margin: 4px 0; }
    .rating-count { font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; }
    .review-count-bar { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .review-count { font-size: 14px; color: #9ca3af; font-weight: 500; }
    .review-count strong { color: #1c1e26; font-weight: 700; }
    .review-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .review-card { background: #fff; border: 1.5px solid #eaecf4; border-radius: 14px; padding: 22px 24px; }
    .review-header { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .review-author-wrap { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .review-avatar { width: 38px; height: 38px; border-radius: 10px; background: #f3f4f8; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .review-author { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #1c1e26; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .review-project { font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af; }
    .review-right { text-align: right; }
    .review-stars { color: #f59e0b; font-size: 15px; }
    .review-date { font-size: 11px; color: #c4c9d9; margin-top: 3px; }
    .review-content { font-size: 14px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.8; }
    .review-actions { display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; gap: 8px; margin-top: 14px; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f8; }
    .review-btn { font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; font-weight: 600; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; }
    .review-btn:hover { color: #2563eb; }
    .review-btn.delete:hover { color: #ef4444; }
    .empty-state { text-align: center; padding: 60px 0; font-size: 15px; color: #c4c9d9; }
    .paging { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 6px; }
    .page-btn { padding: 9px 15px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1.5px solid #e2e5ef; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; background: #fff; text-decoration: none; transition: all .15s; }
    .page-btn:hover { border-color: #2563eb; color: #2563eb; }
    .page-btn.active { background: #2563eb; border-color: #2563eb; color: #fff; }
</style>

<div class="page-header">
    <div class="page-header-inner">
        <h1 class="page-title">리뷰 목록</h1>
        <p class="page-desc">전문가에 대한 솔직한 리뷰를 확인하세요.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<section class="list-section">
    <div class="list-inner">

        <!-- 전문가 요약 -->
        <div class="expert-summary">
            <div class="expert-avatar">👨‍💻</div>
            <div class="expert-info">
                <div class="expert-name">
                    김개발
                    <span class="cert-badge">⭐ 인증</span>
                </div>
                <div class="expert-career">풀스택 개발 · 경력 7년</div>
            </div>
            <div class="expert-rating-box">
                <div class="rating-big">4.8</div>
                <div class="rating-stars">★★★★★</div>
                <div class="rating-count">3개 리뷰</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 리뷰 목록 -->
        <div class="review-count-bar">
            <span class="review-count">총 <strong>3</strong>개의 리뷰</span>
        </div>

        <div class="review-list">

            <div class="review-card">
                <div class="review-header">
                    <div class="review-author-wrap">
                        <div class="review-avatar">👤</div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="review-author">이의뢰</div>
                            <div class="review-project">프로젝트: 쇼핑몰 백엔드 개발</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="review-right">
                        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
                        <div class="review-date">2025.01.15</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="review-content">정말 꼼꼼하고 빠르게 작업해 주셨어요. 요구사항을 잘 이해하고 결과물도 깔끔했습니다.</div>
                <div class="review-actions">
                    <a href="/reviews/1/edit" class="review-btn">수정</a>
                    <form action="/reviews/1/delete" method="POST" style="display:inline;">
                        <button type="submit" class="review-btn delete">삭제</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="review-card">
                <div class="review-header">
                    <div class="review-author-wrap">
                        <div class="review-avatar">👤</div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="review-author">박클라이언트</div>
                            <div class="review-project">프로젝트: 관리자 대시보드 구축</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="review-right">
                        <div class="review-stars">★★★★☆</div>
                        <div class="review-date">2025.01.10</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="review-content">소통이 원활하고 일정도 잘 지켜주셨습니다. 중간에 요구사항이 바뀌었는데도 유연하게 대응해 주셔서 감사했어요.</div>
            </div>

            <div class="review-card">
                <div class="review-header">
                    <div class="review-author-wrap">
                        <div class="review-avatar">👤</div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="review-author">최고객</div>
                            <div class="review-project">프로젝트: API 연동 작업</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="review-right">
                        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
                        <div class="review-date">2025.01.05</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="review-content">기술적으로 매우 뛰어나신 분입니다. 복잡한 API 연동 작업을 깔끔하게 처리해 주셨어요.</div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="paging">
            <a href="/reviews?expertId=1&page=1" class="page-btn active">1</a>
            <a href="/reviews?expertId=1&page=2" class="page-btn">2</a>
            <a href="/reviews?expertId=1&page=3" class="page-btn">다음</a>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

{{> layout/footer}}
